jltl2dstar

Class APMonom2APElements

  • java.lang.Object
    • jltl2dstar.APMonom2APElements
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Iterator<APElement>

    public class APMonom2APElements
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Iterator<APElement>
    Iterator over all APElements that are represented by an APMonom. As every APMonom represents a subset of 2^AP, this allows access to all of the members of this subset.
